Been sitting on this one for a while and got around to finalizing it.

I'd say expect about a 2-minute map but I know y'all going to find a way to beat it in less than 1.

This map is kinda a mishmash of different themes I wanted to try out, so you'll find the stages to be very distinguishable from one another.
